('optional-accessible-menu-project', 'input-and-player-experience', 'project', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Optional Accessible Menu Project', 'Optional project brief: Build a menu/settings prototype with remapping, volume sliders, subtitles toggle, scalable UI, and controller navigation. Build a small, reviewable game prototype to practice ideas from Input and Player Experience. Expected evidence includes a playable prototype or isolated mechanic, controls, rules, and tuning notes, and screenshots or a short playtest observation. Keep it lightweight; the goal is applied practice and clearer portfolio evidence, not a mandatory milestone.', 'This optional practice project turns the surrounding Game Developer topics into a concrete artifact. It gives the learner a clearer target, suggested build path, and review evidence without treating completion as proof of mastery or job readiness.', 137, 'choice', 'input-and-player-experience', 702, 7, 4, 'intermediate', 7, '{"source": "roadmap.sh/game-developer","parentGroup": "input-and-player-experience","projectPolicy": "optional_practice","projectPurpose": "optional_practice","projectKind": "game_project","projectScope": "small_practice_artifact","evidenceRequired": true,"claimLimit": "reviewable_project_evidence_only_not_mastery_or_job_readiness","suggestedSteps": ["define the core loop or mechanic","build the smallest playable slice","test controls and feedback","record tuning decisions"],"expectedEvidence": ["a playable prototype or isolated mechanic","controls, rules, and tuning notes","screenshots or a short playtest observation"],"optionalPractice": true,"milestone": false}'::jsonb, false, true, '["Build a small Accessible Menu Project artifact to practice selected concepts from Input and Player Experience.","Explain the main design, data, tooling, or workflow decisions used in the project.","Validate the project with appropriate evidence such as tests, screenshots, logs, metrics, queries, or review notes.","Document setup, usage, limitations, and at least one follow-up improvement."]'::jsonb, '["A repository, notebook, dashboard, write-up, prototype, or configuration artifact is available for review.","The README or project notes state the project goal, setup steps, usage path, and expected output.","The deliverable includes a playable prototype or isolated mechanic, controls, rules, and tuning notes, and screenshots or a short playtest observation.","The learner records validation evidence such as tests, screenshots, logs, metrics, query results, playtest notes, or manual verification steps.","The review notes identify trade-offs, limitations, and one reasonable next improvement."]'::jsonb),
